short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export and analyze your X bookmarks with AI to get insights that drive action.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of losing track of your valuable X bookmarks? Export X Bookmarks is the ultimate tool for anyone who wants to save, organize, and analyze their X bookmarks with ease.

- Export all your X bookmarks in just a few clicks. Save them in a convenient format to use wherever you need.
- Leverage AI to categorize, summarize, and extract insights from your bookmarks.
- Automatically organize your bookmarks by categories, tags, and more, making it easy to find exactly what you're looking for.
